<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify your email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f7;
            color: #51545e;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f4f4f7;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .email-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #667eea;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #51545e;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background-color: #667eea;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e1e4e8;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .info-box p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #0d47a1;
        }
        .welcome-section {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
        }
        .welcome-section h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .welcome-section p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .email-footer {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e1e4e8;
        }
        .email-footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9095a1;
        }
        .checkmark {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #4caf50;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                padding: 20px 0;
            }
            .email-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .email-header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .email-body {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .button {
                padding: 14px 30px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-content">
            <div class="email-header">
                <h1>‚úâÔ∏è Verify your email</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello and welcome to <strong>Formbar</strong>! üéâ</p>
                <p>We're excited to have you on board. To get started and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" class="button">Verify My Email</a>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <p><strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è Why verify?</strong> Email verification helps us ensure account security and enables us to send you important updates about your account.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="welcome-section">
                    <h2>What's Next?</h2>
                    <p>‚úì Complete your profile</p>
                    <p>‚úì Explore our features</p>
                    <p>‚úì Start building amazing forms</p>
                </div>

                <div class="divider"></div>

                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9095a1;">If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #667eea; word-break: break-all;">{{verifyUrl}}</p>

                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #9095a1; margin-top: 30px;">If you didn't create an account with Formbar, please ignore this email.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-footer">
                <p><strong>Formbar</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

